<li>My heart goes out to you.  Don't hesitate to reach out if you need anything at all.</li>
<li>I'm here for you, whether you need a shoulder to cry on or help with errands.</li>
<li>Please accept my deepest condolences. Let me know how I can support you through this.</li>
<li>I’m sending you strength and offering my help in any way needed.</li>
<li> I'm so sorry for your loss.  Is there anything I can do to help ease the burden?</li>
<li>Thinking of you and offering my help during this challenging time.  Please reach out.</li>
<li> My deepest sympathy. I'm happy to help with anything you need.</li>
<li>Please accept my condolences. Let me know if you need any help with arrangements.</li>
<li> Sending you love and support. I'm available to help in any way I can.</li>
<li> My heart aches for you.  Please let me know if you need me for anything.</li>
